divs: Sighting DetailsI was on my way to a technial advisory meeting on the evening I saw the object. I could not stop because of time constraints, however, someone came on the radio and announced they had seen a ufo. I am not sure of the date and year. It was dark so I suspect the time of the year was toward winter. I worked for Volusia County and went to various meetings between Daytona and Edgewater. When I got to the meeting an engineer also remarked on the ufo. It did not strike as one of our aircraft. I am aware of the Harriot Jet which I love. This craft was very high in the night sky so I could define its shape. I do want to send you some other information. During the eighties, I began drawing pictures of vehicles and what seems to be parts of a ship; also I began to write in symbols. I checked with two psychics 3,000 miles apart and approximately 2-3 years in time frame. They both asked me about the symbols, thinking they may have been Egyptian but they are not. I have since tried to get them interpreted. I attach some of the information.
